{"tid":1058024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子疑失業受困留遺書 車內燒炭亡","createTime":"2019-03-12T09:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T09:35:11.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ba9317d8568627e5025fed1acbf3ad5d51e60daa","tid":1058024,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T09:10:27.000Z","msg":"下午2時許，有警員巡經大埔烏蛟騰郊遊徑一露天停車場時，發現一輛私家車停在場邊，於是上前查看，發現一名年約40歲的男子倒卧車廂內，其時已無知覺，旁邊有一盆燒過的炭，懷疑他燒炭尋死。救護員到場檢驗，證實他已死去超過一日，警方在車內撿獲遺書，內容提及事主因失業問題而尋死，正聯絡其家人了解事件。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」： <a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0La5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=30721342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190312/59360382\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190312%2F59360382&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0La5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=084ea331\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190312%2F59360382&h=8a23f6c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190312/59360382</a>"},{"pid":"efa833f06499ed5c16f764ca962d7b3bc2ee27a5","tid":1058024,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T09:11:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4912183c0a1374b830204b22155b5911e226de6f","tid":1058024,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T09:24:37.000Z","msg":"奴性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee73db83f34ea69af3a4553c56f88dad4b59b8e","tid":